44 Ajjhattattika, Hetuduka
Ajjhattattika, Hetuduka
86.
219Ajjhattaṃ hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nabahiddhā nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Bahiddhā hetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naajjhatto nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā dve…pe…  avigate dve.
220Ajjhattaṃ nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nabahiddhā nanahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Bahiddhā nahetuṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naajjhatto nanahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā dve…pe…  avigate dve.
